item.title: About me
item.description: My name is Danyang Zhang, I go by Jasmine as well. I am originally from Zhengzhou, Henan, China. I am currently a first year Ph.D. student at the Department of Statistics in Iowa State University. I earned my B.S. in China and my M.S. at UT Austin. I enjoyed hiking and traveling in my spare time! :bowtie:
